00057 void TestAlways(int expect, char *buff, log_components_t component, char *string)
00058 {
00059   char compare[2048];
00060   sprintf(compare, "%s: %s", LogComponents[component].comp_str, string);
00061   buff[0] = '\0';
00062   LogAlways(component, "%s", string);
00063   if ((expect && (strcmp(compare, buff) != 0)) || (!expect && (buff[0] != '\0')))
00064     {
00065       LogTest("FAILURE: %s produced \"%s\" expected \"%s\"",
00066               string, buff, compare);
00067       exit(1);
00068     }
00069   LogTest("SUCCESS: %s produced \"%s\"", string, buff);
00070 }
